description: There is always time for tea and a slice of cake.
keywords: Cake,Cherry,Pescatarian,Halal,Seafood free,Soy free,Vegetarian,Tree nut free,Sesame free,Peanut free
name: Cherry Cake Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Preheat oven to 180C. Lightly grease and line a large cake tin with baking paper and set aside.
In a mixing bowl cream butter and sugar together.
Add the eggs one at a time and beat well or until well combined.
In another bowl mix the cherries through the flour and then gradually fold into the butter and caster sugar mixture and mix until well combine.
Pour batter into the cake tin and bake in a moderate oven for about 1 hour or until cooked when a skewer is inserted and comes out clean.
